nodes.text: An unidentified bartender droid operated at the Cluster cantina on Nar Shaddaa circa 30 BBY. It appeared to be a modified protocol droid with a tankard of ale attached to the back of its gray, weathered chassis. It dispensed ale from its fingers, connected by a series of tubes to the tankard.
Another similar-looking protocol droid, sans tankard, served at the establishment.
